{"tid":633093,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"36E女sales愛健身 騷「胸」器selfie誘宅男","createTime":"2018-04-18T03:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T19:17:20.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6afa89ad0cd617a75efd0834066036fc07aab3e1","tid":633093,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:56:19.000Z","msg":"台灣百貨公司銷售員林祐安(Sophia)的歐美版身材，被網民追捧。Sophia期望令自己體態更美，定期記錄自己的生活點滴，每日都投入健身運動。<br />\n<br />\n目前，她在中和環球香氛蠟燭專櫃工作，喜歡交朋友讓自己累積更多經驗，可以認識更多愛美的女性顧客，她本身最大的興趣其實是彩妝及紋繡，未來目標是想開一間個人工作室，希望可以藉由專櫃開放式的空間認識客人，將每名顧客當作自己朋友，讓她們在生活上可以一起擁有自信和美麗。<br />\nSophia說：「自己是一個不折不扣的吃貨，我想吃片世界各地的美食，靠自己的雙手賺錢存錢出國旅遊，然後拍出更多美麗的照片好好享受人生的意義。」<br />\n【小檔案】<br />\n生日：1993年9月24日<br />\n身高：172cm<br />\n三圍：36E/28/38<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》<br />\n「千億莊家」肖建華神秘失蹤，《蘋果》精心炮製互動關係圖，讓大家能理清這名「大刁奇人」在各路權貴當中處於何種地位"},{"pid":"6b6d551285c7c098775fe413484a45e7f0c7ad4d","tid":633093,"uid":19552,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20170220/large/1487592748_5820.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170220%2Flarge%2F1487592748_5820.jpg&h=9fdfa803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20170220/large/1487592749_0492.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170220%2Flarge%2F1487592749_0492.jpg&h=e952a4ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20170220/large/1487592753_3963.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170220%2Flarge%2F1487592753_3963.jpg&h=310d0144&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20170220/large/1487592754_a8c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170